          </div>
          <div style="background:rgba(201,168,76,0.06);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:18px 20px;">
            <div style="font-family:'Arial',sans-serif;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:8px;font-weight:700;">What the Fund Retains</div>
            <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;">
              <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text);padding:6px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-dim);">↑ Spread above 17% from PE debt service rate</li>
              <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text);padding:6px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-dim);">↑ 40% equity income per Gulfstream G550 jet</li>
