                <li><span class="lv-label">Asset Expertise</span><span class="lv-val">Credit, Aviation, PE, Art, Mining</span></li>
                <li><span class="lv-label">Co-Investment</span><span class="lv-val td-green">Yes — Personal Capital (amount disclosed under NDA)</span></li>
                <li><span class="lv-label">Management Fee</span><span class="lv-val td-green">None Charged</span></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <h4>Domain Expertise</h4>
        <div>
          <span class="tag tag-gold">Structured Private Credit</span>
          <span class="tag tag-gold">PE Sponsor Lending</span>
          <span class="tag tag-gold">UCC-1 Lien Perfection &amp; Enforcement</span>
