        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Dark Horse Platform — Organizational Overview</h3>
        <p>Dark Horse Wealth Management serves as the <strong>governing private family office</strong> for the entire Caraway investment ecosystem — the top-tier management and strategy entity overseeing a growing constellation of investment vehicles and operating entities spanning private credit, mineral resources, aviation, and investment banking advisory. The Dark Horse platform provides institutional infrastructure — fund administration, legal, banking, and tax services — to each underlying entity, ensuring every fund operates to institutional standard regardless of its current AUM.</p>
        <br>
        <p>Draft Horse Capital Partners is the <strong>institutional-grade structured credit vehicle</strong> within the Dark Horse platform, purpose-built for accredited investors who require UCC-1 collateral protection, third-party administration and audit, and quarterly income distribution at yields that compensate for the commitment made.</p>
